~Tutorial (Interference Edition)~

The goal of the interference event is to rescue the heroine.
If successful, you can avoid the NTR event that would occur
that week. On the other hand, if you fail even once, a
tragic ending awaits. Everything depends on you. Please
decide the fate of the story with your own hands.

Afterwards, I somehow managed to escape to the vicinity of
my home. To check on Asahi's safety, I hid near the house.
After waiting a few minutes, Asahi returned from the
direction of the next town, still wet.

I casually struck up a conversation with Asahi to subtly
check on her clothes. She answered that she got wet due to a
sprinkler malfunctioning in a shop she entered to meet an
acquaintance.

It seems the small fire strategy worked just as I thought it
would. I wanted to hear more details, but Asahi said she
wanted to change out of her wet clothes and quickly went
inside the house.

I feel bad for the shop, but I'm really glad nothing
happened to Asahi. Completely relieved, I went home in a
great mood. Perhaps due to the exhaustion from the day's
events in the neighboring town, I slept soundly until
morning.
